2932
01:57:46.154 --> 01:57:48.794
su risa era de una escandalosa sonoridad.

2933
01:57:49.514 --> 01:57:50.634
Con Denouilleur

2934
01:57:50.634 --> 01:57:52.553
se mostraba taciturno y aplicado,

2935
01:57:53.128 --> 01:57:55.369
