19252
12:35:11.582 --> 12:35:12.862
La noche húmeda,

19253
12:35:12.942 --> 12:35:13.822
la lluvia,

19254
12:35:14.222 --> 12:35:15.662
el tiempo excitador,

19255
12:35:15.742 --> 12:35:18.542
